findStrings.find: SELECT hr, new_uv, uj_ct, uv_ct, pv_ct FROM ( SELECT toHour(stt) as hr, sum(pv_ct) AS pv_ct, sum(sv_ct) AS sv_ct , sum(dur_sum) AS dur_sum FROM dws_traffic_vc_ch_ar_is_new_page_view_window WHERE toYYYYMMDD(stt) = ? GROUP BY toHour(stt) ) pv JOIN ( SELECT toHour(stt) as hr, sum(uv_ct) AS uv_ct ,sum(if(is_new = '1', dws_traffic_vc_ch_ar_is_new_page_view_window.uv_ct, 0)) AS new_uv FROM dws_traffic_vc_ch_ar_is_new_page_view_window WHERE toYYYYMMDD(stt) = ? GROUP BY toHour(stt) ) uv ON pv.is_new = uv.is_new LEFT JOIN ( SELECT toHour(stt) as hr, sum(uj_ct) AS uj_ct FROM dws_traffic_vc_ch_ar_is_new_page_view_window WHERE toYYYYMMDD(stt) = ? GROUP BY toHour(stt) ) uj ON pv.is_new = uj.is_new
